@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - US263 Detect Drone Collisions in Real Time

autonumber

actor "Drone Operator" as Operator
participant ":System" as System

activate Operator

Operator -> System: start show monitoring
activate System

loop for each timestamp
System -> System: process drone positions
alt collision detected (distance < combined radius)
System --> Operator: alert (visual: "ðŸ’¥ Collision detected...")
System -> System: log collision event in Collision_Stamp
System -> System: send SIGUSR1 to involved drones
else no collision
System --> Operator: update drone positions (normal status)
end alt
end loop

Operator -> System: stop show monitoring
deactivate System

deactivate Operator

note right: Updated as of 11:12 AM WEST on Friday, May 16, 2025.\n- Collision detection uses distance < (biggestDimension/200 + 0.5m).\n- Drones marked as terminated are excluded.\n- Visual alert is a terminal message.

@enduml